c: 3
v: 73
t: "And believe no one except the one who follows your religion. Say (O Muhammad SAW): \"Verily! Right guidance is the Guidance of Allah\" and do not believe that anyone can receive like that which you have received (of Revelation) except when he follows your religion, otherwise they would engage you in argument before your Lord. Say (O Muhammad SAW): \"All the bounty is in the Hand of Allah; He grants to whom He wills. And Allah is All-Sufficient for His creatures' needs, the All-Knower"